{
  "stem": "1736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to go there quite regularly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, I didn't say before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to go regularly to Dessau to cheder anyhow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a weekly or biweekly situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to get on my bike and ride the 15 kilometers there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It depends how I went, and it depends on the of the year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes it might take me half an hour, particularly if I got hold of a bus and hung on to the back of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other times, if it was snowing, and-- you had walk part of the time, so-- you know, but it might have taken an hour or something like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was an [INAUDIBLE] of 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not sure of the numbers, but it was a very wealthy congregation, money left to it by some previous congregants.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but I can't give you the numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was-- like I said, it had a beautiful synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, it was-- it was just the one big synagogue, which took up a whole sort of city block, and consisted of not only the ordinary synagogue.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a small synagogue which was used during ordinary week prayers, when, you know, they couldn't fill the main hall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Attached to it was a building with social halls for weddings, and bar mitzvah, and these sort of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there was a residence of the rabbi attached to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think one of the teachers lived there as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the whole thing was built round-- on this block with a big center court where there were gardens inside.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
